# wasm-pack regenerates these; we commit them so pnpm workspace link
# resolves in fresh checkouts (CI, cold clones) without needing a Rust
# toolchain + wasm-pack install just to run `pnpm install`.
#
# Track: package.json, *.js, *.d.ts, *.wasm, BUILD.bazel
# Ignore: transient wasm-pack scratch files
.wasm-pack.log
*.tmp
